        <mxCell id="d1" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8f9fa;strokeColor=#dee2e6;fontSize=9;arcSize=8;strokeWidth=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=5;spacingRight=6;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;⚡ Activities&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;• Questions — ask until idea is fully understood&lt;br&gt;• Research — spawn parallel domain agents&lt;br&gt;• Requirements — extract v1/v2 scope&lt;br&gt;• Roadmap — create phased plan&lt;/font&gt;&lt;hr style=&quot;border:0;border-top:1px solid #ccc;margin:5px 0 3px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;📄 Artifacts&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px; color: #555;&quot;&gt;PROJECT.md&lt;br&gt;REQUIREMENTS.md&lt;br&gt;ROADMAP.md&lt;br&gt;STATE.md&lt;br&gt;.planning/research/&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
