        <mxCell id="d2" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8f9fa;strokeColor=#dee2e6;fontSize=9;arcSize=8;strokeWidth=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=5;spacingRight=6;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;⚡ Activities&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;• Analyze phase for gray areas&lt;br&gt;• Identify visual/API/content decisions&lt;br&gt;• Capture preferences &amp;amp; decisions&lt;br&gt;• Shape implementation vision&lt;/font&gt;&lt;hr style=&quot;border:0;border-top:1px solid #ccc;margin:5px 0 3px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;📄 Artifacts&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px; color: #555;&quot;&gt;{N}-CONTEXT.md&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="195" width="190" x="355" y="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="d3" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8f9fa;strokeColor=#dee2e6;fontSize=9;arcSize=8;strokeWidth=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=5;spacingRight=6;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;⚡ Activities&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;• Research implementation approaches&lt;br&gt;• Create 2-3 atomic task plans (XML)&lt;br&gt;• Verify plans against requirements&lt;br&gt;• Loop until plans pass checker&lt;/font&gt;&lt;hr style=&quot;border:0;border-top:1px solid #ccc;margin:5px 0 3px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;📄 Artifacts&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px; color: #555;&quot;&gt;{N}-RESEARCH.md&lt;br&gt;{N}-{M}-PLAN.md&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="210" width="190" x="575" y="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="d4" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8f9fa;strokeColor=#dee2e6;fontSize=9;arcSize=8;strokeWidth=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=5;spacingRight=6;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;⚡ Activities&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;• Run plans in parallel waves&lt;br&gt;• Fresh 200K context per plan&lt;br&gt;• Atomic commit per task&lt;br&gt;• Verify against phase goals&lt;/font&gt;&lt;hr style=&quot;border:0;border-top:1px solid #ccc;margin:5px 0 3px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;📄 Artifacts&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px; color: #555;&quot;&gt;{N}-{M}-SUMMARY.md&lt;br&gt;{N}-VERIFICATION.md&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="210" width="190" x="795" y="140" as="geometry" />
